{"tid":2444621,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"用中文 SEND EMAIL 比上司鬧……","createTime":"2021-03-13T03:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T01:24:38.000Z","uid":73381,"like":17,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b12050aaa103da43744b74fe3a4b6f9e58217957","tid":2444621,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"今日有啲唔舒服，個腦唔係好轉到，咁啱隔離部門啲人 SEND EMAIL 比我，咁規矩就一定會 CC 埋比兩邊上司，咁我真係頭痛到諗唔嘢，又見係自己公司，咪索性用中文應佢囉&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n點知冇幾耐之後上司叫我入房，問我點解會用中文應 EMAIL，佢話公司不成文規矩係一定要用英文應 EMAIL，對內對外都唔可以用中文，唔係就好似好冇文化冇教養咁，會比其他部門以為我哋冇教養&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我真係好想知點解用中文應 EMAIL 就係冇文化冇教養呢？<br />\n成間公司都係中國人，又冇外國人，又冇其他唔同詞言嘅人，點解一定要用英文 SEND EMAIL&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9c27d955f432fe2d4ead6dd4c0446bed642b26ea","tid":2444621,"uid":60279,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"答佢星期六都要番工既低賤公司入面d人係咁低賤<br />\n一定要用低賤語言先得"},{"pid":"55c6ba7d68ce93b7e8ec508cddbf2145ed8788e1","tid":2444621,"uid":224533,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"香港法定語言係中英文"},{"pid":"3790fc72aad8914486ee1c4aaf60ed42586bc801","tid":2444621,"uid":116723,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"報國安 熱線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51ff7a1523f800b990a2e2dc46480d7d5b01625","tid":2444621,"uid":12628,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"樓主打左你媽死了"},{"pid":"1b54e3670a1b8574574f15ff33d389a611ca89c8","tid":2444621,"uid":101845,"like":32,"dislike":9,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"得大陸人先會用中文email"},{"pid":"2cd3483ff6f3c34b05a2e372ded1df12f5bb2799","tid":2444621,"uid":17606,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"啲港燦成日以為自己用英文就高人一等咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6010ab4d41f00a5d00f9468afb46c60fc85e425a","t